  <title>Disable sounds</title>

  <p>When sounds are enabled, you will hear something every time a marble is
  dropped, or when a game ends.</p>

  <steps>
    <title>To disable sounds:</title>
    <item>
      <p>Press the menu button in the top-right corner of the window and uncheck
      <gui style="menuitem">Sound</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Close the menu by clicking outside of the menu.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

